    "description": "<i>I have always dreamt of being a storyteller. As a young man I used to tell stories to my younger brothers and imagine the fantastical journey my words would take us all on.<br><br> So please join me, and let me tell you a story.</i><br><br>Welcome to Signals to EV is a narrative driven adventure game inspired by “Getting Over It with Bennet Foddy”. However instead of being a punishing game about starting over, Signals to EV is a more casual relaxing experience. This game was made because I wanted to tell stories. I hope that you’ll find something to enjoy about it and maybe even a lesson to take away. If you do, that's wonderful. Thank you for letting me share this experience with you. If you don't, that's okay too, thank you for trusting me with your time and attention.<br><br>Either way thank you , for soaking up the music, listening to the stories, and in the end choosing the path that's right for you. <br><br>Travel the world searching for human memories<br>Listen to the stories of humans gone by<br>Unravel the mysteries of Mothership and EV<br>Multiple endings and secrets to discover <br>Relaxing and calming adventure<br>Passive aggressive overseer",
